{"tid":1396273,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"參與今晚遮打「公僕仝人，與民同行」集會的朋友留意","createTime":"2019-08-02T04:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:07:32.000Z","uid":267757,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f879b452babbe2549a47771c0ac927ad3f3cdcd","tid":1396273,"uid":267757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"(轉)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pieMcii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpieMcii.jpg&h=9e2eabc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【緊急！請廣傳🙏】公務員要爬山了！<br />\n<br />\n☆守護公務員♡溫馨提示<br />\n集會時：<br />\n1. 唔好叫任何官員下台<br />\n2. 唔好提任何獨立字眼<br />\n3. 如遇搞事者，請大叫「公務員，加油！」<br />\n4. 唔好出示任何國家/地方旗幟<br />\n5. 在集會範圍內，派罷工傳單或呼叫罷工，會對公務員構成威脅。如果要派，麻煩請在其他地方<br />\n6. 請諒解公務員不能收受利益，不會接受籌款/捐款<br />\n7. 呼籲多D人出席，對公務員來說，越多人便越安全<br />\n<br />\n公務員自己出錢出力，仲犧牲前途站出來。集會期間和完場後，都必須和平、理性、非暴力。兄弟姊妹們，齊撐公務員！"},{"pid":"ad935889d9ec800c0c267c987c717fd22e1c22dc","tid":1396273,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"派罷工傳單都唔得？"},{"pid":"8e14f85be05ea9cc8993a23c6c367e427ff06710","tid":1396273,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:49:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我地可以迫大集團表態，<br />\n只要佢地肯表態唔反對，<br />\n市民自然會少左個包袱去罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一信 推到 大貓 今日內交代 8月5罷工 立場！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMiNLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMiNLW.jpg&h=611f7a48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eec3ee91bad32929c7a6a6b726c8bcdcbbeb7e60","tid":1396273,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:50:18.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n會過來坐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"